## 🔌 API Reference

Your backend server provides APIs that the React frontend uses. Here are the main ones:

### Data Management APIs

**Upload files:**
```
POST /api/upload
Body: FormData with files and metadata
```

**Convert Excel to JSON:**
```
POST /api/convert-excel
Body: FormData with .xlsx file
```

### Embeddings APIs

**Create embeddings (regular):**
```
POST /api/create-embeddings
Body: { files: ["file1.json", "file2.json"] }
```

**Create embeddings (fast batch):**
```
POST /api/create-embeddings-batch
Body: { 
  files: ["file1.json"], 
  scriptName: "create-embeddings-batch-mistral.js",
  jobType: "embeddings"
}
```

### Search APIs

**Vector/Semantic Search:**
```
POST /api/search/vector
Body: { query: "login test", limit: 10 }
Response: [{ id, title, description, score, embedding }, ...]
```

**BM25/Keyword Search:**
```
POST /api/search/bm25
Body: { query: "login test", limit: 10 }
Response: [{ id, title, description, score }, ...]
```

**Hybrid Search:**
```
POST /api/search/hybrid
Body: { query: "login test", limit: 10 }
Response: [Merged results from Vector + BM25]
```

**Reranked Search:**
```
POST /api/search/rerank
Body: { query: "login test", limit: 10 }
Response: [Results reranked by AI]
```

### Utility APIs

**Health Check:**
```
GET /api/health
Response: { status: "ok", timestamp: "..." }
```

**Get job status:**
```
GET /api/jobs/:jobId
Response: { id, status, progress, eta, created, started, completed }
```

